==English==
===Etymology===
From Latin ''[[ventralis]]'', "ventral", from ''[[venter]]'', "abdomen", "stomach", "belly"
===Adjective===
'''ventral'''
# related to the [[abdomen]] or [[stomach]]
# on the front side of the human body or the according surface of an animal
# An anatomical term referring to the bottom portion of either foot and/or hand.
====Translations====
